POD: Pod is smallest building block or basic unit of scheduling in Kubernetes.
      Pod represent smallest runnig process.
      Each Pod will have unique IP Address 

kubectl get pods
kubectl get pods -o wide

Pod Types
==========
1) One-container-per-pod
2) Multicontainer-pod or side car
      Ex: log shippers, Monitoring agents, Init Container

Static Pod: Static Pods are directly managed by kubelet and API server doest not have any control over these static Pods.
            Kubelet is responsible for Static pod and it restarts if static pod goes down.
Ex: control plane pods (API Server, Control Manager, ETCD, scheduler)


sudo ls /ect/kubernetes/manifests/
